        <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Ilustración: consecuencia ruido">
          <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#fff7f3"/>
          <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="none" stroke="#c94a3f" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="100" cy="60" r="18" fill="#ffd6d2"/>
            <text x="10" y="120" font-size="10" fill="#c94a3f">Ruido estresante</text>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="translation">Consequence: Loud speakers stress wildlife and disrupt their behavior; the noise can diminish the experience for other visitors.</div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Rule 13 -->
  <article class="rule-card" id="r13">
    <div class="rule-left">
      <div class="rule-text">Recuerde siempre revisar y respetar los horarios de visita.</div>
      <div class="img-wrap">
        <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Ilustración: respetar horarios">
          <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#f3fbff"/>
          <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="none" stroke="#2b7a6b" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="70" y="30" width="40" height="40" rx="6" fill="#dff3ee"/>
            <text x="10" y="120" font-size="10" fill="#1f5a48">Respetar horarios</text>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="translation">Always remember to check and respect visiting hours.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="rule-right">
      <div class="consequence">Consecuencia: No respetar horarios puede interferir con labores de conservación, monitoreo y seguridad; además expone a los visitantes a riesgos por falta de vigilancia.</div>
      <div class="img-wrap">
        <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Ilustración: consecuencia horarios">
          <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#fff7f3"/>
          <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="none" stroke="#c94a3f" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="70" y="30" width="40" height="40" rx="6" fill="#ffd6d2"/>
            <text x="10" y="120" font-size="10" fill="#c94a3f">Interferencia en conservación</text>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="translation">Consequence: Failure to adhere to the schedule may interfere with conservation, monitoring, and safety efforts; it also exposes visitors to risks due to a lack of supervision.</div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- REMINDERS section -->
  <section style="margin-top:18px">
    <div class="reminder-banner" role="note" aria-label="Recordar">
