      <div style="font-weight:700;color:var(--accent-dark)">Visite los sitios acompañado de un guía especializado — Visit protected areas with a specialized guide.</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Reminder 1 -->
    <article class="rule-card" id="rem1">
      <div class="rule-left">
        <div class="rule-text">Visite los sitios acompañado de un guía especializado</div>
        <div class="img-wrap">
          <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#f3fbf9"/>
            <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="#bfe9d9" stroke="#2b7a6b">
              <circle cx="40" cy="60" r="12"/>
              <rect x="80" y="40" width="60" height="30" rx="6"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="translation">Visit protected areas with a specialized guide.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-right">
        <div class="consequence">Consecuencias: Ir sin guía aumenta el riesgo de daño al entorno por desconocimiento de rutas, especies sensibles y prácticas de bajo impacto; se incrementan las probabilidades de pisar hábitats frágiles, molestar fauna o introducir riesgos accidentales.</div>
        <div class="img-wrap">
          <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#fff7f3"/>
            <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="#ffd6d2" stroke="#c94a3f">
              <circle cx="40" cy="60" r="12"/>
              <rect x="80" y="40" width="60" height="30" rx="6"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="translation">Consequences: Hiking without a guide increases the risk of environmental damage due to a lack of knowledge about trails, sensitive species, and low-impact practices; it also increases the likelihood of trampling fragile habitats, disturbing wildlife, or introducing accidental risks.</div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Reminder 2 -->
    <article class="rule-card" id="rem2">
      <div class="rule-left">
        <div class="rule-text">No escriba frases en el entorno natural</div>
        <div class="img-wrap">
          <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#f3fbff"/>
            <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="#dff3ee" stroke="#2b7a6b">
              <rect x="30" y="40" width="40" height="20" rx="4"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="translation">Do not write on the landscape</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-right">
        <div class="consequence">Consecuencias: Escribir o tallar en rocas, troncos o conchas daña superficies que pueden ser microhábitats o elementos geológicos únicos; el vandalismo altera el valor estético y científico del lugar.</div>
        <div class="img-wrap">
          <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#fff7f3"/>
            <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="#ffd6d2" stroke="#c94a3f">
              <rect x="30" y="40" width="40" height="20" rx="4"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="translation">Consequences: Writing or carving on rocks, logs, or shells damages surfaces that may serve as microhabitats or unique geological features; vandalism detracts from the site’s aesthetic and scientific value.</div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Reminder 3 -->
    <article class="rule-card" id="rem3">
      <div class="rule-left">
        <div class="rule-text">Use servicios turísticos autorizados</div>
        <div class="img-wrap">
          <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#f6fbf9"/>
            <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="#bfe9d9" stroke="#2b7a6b">
              <rect x="30" y="40" width="40" height="20" rx="4"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="translation">Use authorized tourism services.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-right">
        <div class="consequence">Consecuencias: Contratar operadores no autorizados puede implicar prácticas sin medidas de conservación (anclajes inadecuados, rutas fuera de zonas permitidas, manejo inexperto), lo que daña arrecifes, playas y fauna.</div>
        <div class="img-wrap">
          <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#fff7f3"/>
            <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="#ffd6d2" stroke="#c94a3f">
              <rect x="30" y="40" width="40" height="20" rx="4"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="translation">Consequences: Hiring unauthorized operators may result in practices that lack conservation measures (inappropriate anchoring, routes outside permitted areas, inexperienced handling), which damages reefs, beaches, and wildlife.</div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Reminder 4 -->
    <article class="rule-card" id="rem4">
      <div class="rule-left">
        <div class="rule-text">Deje la basura clasificada en su lugar</div>
        <div class="img-wrap">
          <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#f3fbff"/>
            <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="#dff3ee" stroke="#2b7a6b">
              <rect x="40" y="40" width="30" height="40" rx="6"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="translation">Leave the classified trash in its place.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-right">
        <div class="consequence">Consecuencias: No clasificar o abandonar residuos contamina suelos y aguas, atrae especies invasoras y pone en riesgo a fauna que puede ingerir o enredarse en desechos; la acumulación altera procesos ecológicos.</div>
        <div class="img-wrap">
          <svg class="svg-ill" viewBox="0 0 200 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect rx="10" width="200" height="140" fill="#fff7f3"/>
            <g transform="translate(12,18)" fill="#ffd6d2" stroke="#c94a3f">
              <rect x="40" y="40" width="30" height="40" rx="6"/>
