          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="translation">Consequences: Failing to properly dispose of or abandoning waste pollutes soil and water, attracts invasive species, and endangers wildlife that may ingest or become entangled in the debris; the accumulation of waste disrupts ecological processes.</div>
      </div>
    </article>

  </section>

